name: Splinterlands UNTAMED! A Blockchain Trading Card Game!
description: Splinterlands.io goes physical: stickers, shirts, book, printed decks, and the new edition - UNTAMED! The scorched land beneath you seems to breath fire and smoke. You try to hustle your family along before the flowing lava dissolves you or the ember-filled sky blackens, burning your flesh and lungs. Just behind the ridge you can hear the ravenous wolves howling as they hunt what's left of your clan. In the far off distance you see torrential rain and likely floods. You know no peace. There's survival or death, but no luxury. No home.
